column2: Analogue: A Hate Story Ep. 1 - Two Families
column7:
Welcome to my Let's Play of Analogue: A Hate Story, a visual novel by Christine Love. Join me as I investigate what happened to a ship that has been missing for hundreds of years.

Learn more about the game from the main site:
http://ahatestory.com/

column2: Analogue: A Hate Story Ep. 7 - Exploring Alternative Endings
column7:
Welcome to my Let's Play of Analogue: A Hate Story, a visual novel by Christine Love. Join me as I investigate what happened to a ship that has been missing for hundreds of years. This is a followup episode where I revisit the game and check out some of the other endings.
